data.description: The Woodridge community in the ever-desired City of Blaine boasts the best homesites in new construction. The serene views with mature trees and ponds throughout the community is the perfect spot for anyone looking for space behind your home. Conveniently placed near Lexington Ave. and easy access to 35W and 35E. Blaine hosts some of the best recreational activities you will find. The national sports center has leagues for every interest whether it be hockey, basketball, soccer, lacrosse, rugby, and indoor baseball training. The brand-new Sunrise elementary is walking distance and features a great park for any age. Dining is almost second to none, with great spots like The Tavern, Bricks, and Roadside just to name a few. Projected to close in November/December.
